       <p1>The BMW R 1250 GS is a versatile adventure motorcycle manufactured <br> by BMW Motorrad in Berlin, Germany.Here are some key details about it:</p1><br>
      <p2>&copy;Engine: The R 1250 GS features a 1,254 cc (76.5 cu in) two-cylinder boxer engine <br> with four valves per cylinder and variable valve timing (VVT).<br> This innovative ShiftCam engine design provides smooth power delivery and<br>  excellent performance.</p2>  <br>
      <p3>&copy;Features:
        LED flashing turn indicators come standard.<br> 
        Optional features include Cruising Light, handlebar risers (30 mm),<br>  and an enduro package for off-road adventures.
        Comfortable heated seat.<br> 
        Adaptive headlight with LED technology.<br> 
        Ride Modes Pro and ECO Modes.<br> 
        Dynamic Traction Control (DTC) and ABS Pro.<br> 
        Connectivity with a TFT display and USB remote positive terminal.</p3>

